= SDL_GetSystemRAM =
Use this function to get the amount of RAM configured in the system.




== Syntax ==
<syntaxhighlight lang='c++'>
int SDL_GetSystemRAM(void)
</syntaxhighlight>


== Return Value ==
Returns the amount of RAM configured in the system in MB.



